'''Sambab''', '''Sanbab''' ({{lang-en|lung}}; {{lang-ar|رئة}}) (wadarteedu tahay '''Sambabo'''; magaca [[Saynis]]: pulmonarius) waa xubnaha [[neefsi]]ga ee [[dad]]ka iyo [[xayawaan]]ka. 
[[Naasley]]da iyo dhamaan noocyada kale ee [[noole|noolaha]] [[labo|labada Sambab]] waxay ku leeyihiin [[laab]]ta dhexdeeda, gaar ahaan meel u dhow [[wadne|wadnaha]]. 

Sambabadu waxay ka tirsan yihiin qaab-dhismeedka [[ubuc]]da [[jidh]]ka [[noole|noolaha]], waana xubin muhiim u ah jiritaanka iyo nolosha dhamaan noolaha. 

Shaqada ugu wayn ee Sambabadu waa ineey soo ururiyaan [[hawo|hawada]] [[ogsajiin]]ta ku jirta [[cir]]ka ayadoo soo dhex maraysa [[san]]ka, dhuunta ilaa sambabada oo u sii gubiya [[xidid]]dada [[dhiig]]a qaada ilaa dhamaan unugyada jidhka. Sidoo kale, dib uga soo qaadaan [[unug]]yada [[hawo|hawada]] eey isticmaaleen ee [[Kaarboon|kaarboon-labo-ogsaydh]]. 

